Flogiston
=========

REQUIREMENTS:

  - Requires Rails 2.3 stable or later.
  - Requires rspec, rspec-rails, and mocha to run tests.

INSTALLATION:

   Installation as a stand-alone application:

   % git clone git://github.com/flogic/flogiston.git


   Installation as a plugin in a Rails application:

   % script/plugin install git://github.com/flogic/flogiston.git


POST-INSTALLATION:

 - rake gems:install
 - rake gems:unpack
 - rake gems:build
 - rake db:migrate


